author: cbs8
title: Lake Charles woman named Miss Louisiana USA
text:
LAFAYETTE, La. (AP) - A 21-year-old from Lake Charles has been crowned Miss Louisiana USA, and a 16-year-old is Miss Louisiana Teen USA.
The Advertiser ( http://bit.ly/1RuMg9q ) reports that Maaliyah Papillion will represent Louisiana in the 2016 Miss USA pageant, and Ellie Picone will be in the Miss Teen USA contest.
The pageants were held Saturday at the Heymann Performing Arts Center in Lafayette.
Information from: The Advertiser, http://www.theadvertiser.com
